metadata.name: The Alchemist
metadata.description:
The alchemist transforms or creates something through a seemingly magical process, she performs a form of chemistry from the Middle Ages which was concerned with transforming various metals into gold, from the art you would notice she has a lot of gold on her. 

The hour glass on her head reminds her  the speed  with which every moment of life passes by, and how human existence is fleeting, and that the  ‘sands of time’  will run out for every human life, although, An alchemist is said to believe that life is prolonged through transmutation

She Carries  around the eagle which reconnects her with her spiritual path, it leads the way for her and brings powerful connection and messages from the source of creation. 

Lastly, she resides in the desert during the periods she needs to reflect, as the emptiness of the desert creates strength for her.
